<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Farm Machine Riddles</title>
<style>
body{
font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
background:#e8f5e9;
text-align:center;
padding:30px;
}

h1{
color:#2e7d32;
}

.riddle{
background:white;
border-radius:10px;
padding:20px;
margin:15px auto;
max-width:500px;
box-shadow:0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

button{
background:#4caf50;
color:white;
border:none;
padding:10px 15px;
border-radius:5px;
cursor:pointer;
margin-top:10px;
}

.answer{
display:none;
font-weight:bold;
color:#1b5e20;
margin-top:10px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<h1>🚜 Farm Machinery Riddles</h1>
<p>Read the riddle and click to see the answer!</p>

<div class="riddle">
<p>I am big and strong. I have big wheels. Farmers drive me in the field. What am I?</p>
<button onclick="showAnswer(1)">Show Answer</button>
<p class="answer" id="a1">Tractor</p>
</div>

<div class="riddle">
<p>I cut wheat and corn. I collect the grain. I work in big fields. What am I?</p>
<button onclick="showAnswer(2)">Show Answer</button>
<p class="answer" id="a2">Combine Harvester</p>
</div>

<div class="riddle">
<p>I plant small seeds in the soil. I work with a tractor. Plants grow in lines. What am I?</p>
<button onclick="showAnswer(3)">Show Answer</button>
<p class="answer" id="a3">Seed Planter</p>
</div>

<div class="riddle">
<p>I spray water or chemicals on plants. I help crops stay healthy. What am I?</p>
<button onclick="showAnswer(4)">Show Answer</button>
<p class="answer" id="a4">Sprayer</p>
</div>

<div class="riddle">
<p>I dig and turn the soil before planting. A tractor pulls me. What am I?</p>
<button onclick="showAnswer(5)">Show Answer</button>
<p class="answer" id="a5">Plow</p>
</div>

<div class="riddle">
<p>I cut grass to make food for cows. Farmers use me in the field. What am I?</p>
<button onclick="showAnswer(6)">Show Answer</button>
<p class="answer" id="a6">Mower</p>
</div>

<div class="riddle">
<p>I make round or square hay blocks for animals. What am I?</p>
<button onclick="showAnswer(7)">Show Answer</button>
<p class="answer" id="a7">Baler</p>
</div>

<div class="riddle">
<p>A tractor pulls me. I carry crops or tools around the farm. What am I?</p>
<button onclick="showAnswer(8)">Show Answer</button>
<p class="answer" id="a8">Trailer</p>
</div>

<div class="riddle">
<p>I lift heavy things like hay or soil. I have two arms in front. What am I?</p>
<button onclick="showAnswer(9)">Show Answer</button>
<p class="answer" id="a9">Front Loader</p>
</div>

<div class="riddle">
<p>I break the soil into small pieces after plowing. What am I?</p>
<button onclick="showAnswer(10)">Show Answer</button>
<p class="answer" id="a10">Harrow</p>
</div>

<div class="riddle">
<p>I give water to plants in big circles in the field. What am I?</p>
<button onclick="showAnswer(11)">Show Answer</button>
<p class="answer" id="a11">Irrigation Machine</p>
</div>

<div class="riddle">
<p>I collect cotton from plants in big fields. What am I?</p>
<button onclick="showAnswer(12)">Show Answer</button>
<p class="answer" id="a12">Cotton Harvester</p>
</div>

<script>
function showAnswer(num){
document.getElementById("a"+num).style.display="block";
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
